LAYOUT CONCEPTS:

PRELOADER:
Full viewport, navy background var(--color-bg-brand).
Logo centred, fades up from slight below and settles.
Gold rule var(--color-accent) extends beneath logo
left to right. Brief stillness — let it breathe.
Two panels split simultaneously: top lifts, bottom drops,
revealing the site. Total 2 seconds maximum.
Dispatch preloader:complete event on finish.
GSAP file: preloader.gsap.ts

BUTTON:
Three variants: primary, secondary, ghost.
Square corners — var(--radius-none). No pill shape ever.
DM Sans, var(--font-size-sm), var(--font-weight-medium),
var(--letter-spacing-wide), uppercase.
Padding: var(--space-sm) block, var(--space-xl) inline.
Primary: var(--color-bg-brand) fill, var(--color-text-inverse),
  darkens to var(--color-brand-mid) on hover.
Secondary: transparent, var(--color-brand) border and text,
  fills var(--color-bg-brand) with inverse text on hover.
Ghost: transparent, white border and text,
  fills white with var(--color-brand) text on hover.
  Ghost is only for use on dark backgrounds.
No GSAP.

SECTION:
Pure layout wrapper. No horizontal padding.
Background and vertical padding only.
data-theme variants:
  light   → var(--color-bg)
  subtle  → var(--color-bg-subtle)
  dark    → var(--color-bg-brand)
  accent  → var(--color-bg-accent)
Default padding-block: var(--space-section).
data-size="sm" → var(--space-3xl).
data-size="lg" → var(--space-5xl).
No GSAP.

CONTAINER:
Width constraint only. No colour, no vertical spacing.
Responsive padding-inline at all three breakpoints.
data-width variants:
  narrow  → max-width var(--width-narrow)
  content → max-width var(--width-content) (default)
  wide    → max-width var(--width-wide)
Always margin-inline: auto.
No GSAP.

NAVBAR:
Fixed, full width, z-index high.
Transparent background on load — sits over hero image.
Gains var(--color-bg-brand) background and 1px
var(--color-border-brand) bottom border on scroll
past 40px. JS adds .is-scrolled class.
Logo left — white SVG filter on dark bg.
Nav links centre-right: uppercase DM Sans, font-size-sm,
  wide tracking, white, gold underline extends on hover.
Phone number far right as ghost-style outlined button.
Hide nav links and phone on mobile — show hamburger only.
Mobile menu: full-screen navy overlay, large Cormorant
  Garamond link names (font-size-4xl, light weight)
  stagger in on open. Address line at bottom.
GSAP file: navbar.gsap.ts

